name: Blue_Mint1
description: Loose sketches of girl figures caught in a flow of emotions. A bit of hope on top of resignation, hesitation and melancholy. Exploration of flow, hand drawing, fast sketches and visible paint strokes. Created fully digitally in Photoshop. Mint 1 (out of 6) Edition of 5  Edition 1 is the most figurative one - Girl sketches are brought to the front and catch most attention, this is least experimental Edition  Warsaw, FuzOne 30 04 2021
